    public class MultiSelectSpinner<T>
extends android.widget.Spinner
implements android.content.DialogInterface.OnMultiChoiceClickListener
    A view that extends Spinner and allows to choose multiple items. Selected values are displayed on the spinner divided by comma.
    Since:
    1.0
